        id: 53,
        name: "",
        url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dytb4ayqj/image/upload/v1698879408/Screen_Shot_2023-11-01_at_6.56.17_PM_suxtha.png",
        abovewriting:
          "WEDNESDAY: Today I worked on the cave falling scene. I added the notepad with cross offs on object collection, change gravity scale on animation trigger. I made the mistake of trying to add a bool to a script that is attached to the items spawning, I finally realized after researching that I needed to attach it to a single pervasive object, so I put it on the background.",
        belowwriting:
          "I also added colliders to the sides of the hole, stopped spawning objects once all objects are collected and player will land, fixed the issue with the inventory button not changing to open in this scene, and added a platform to the bottom of the scene. I'm trying to keep track of my progress daily so I can better determine how much I'm able to get done each week in the future. I want to get at least this first chapter mostly done by November 28th, for the gallery show at school.",
        created_at: "2023-11-01T22:57:59.766Z",
        updated_at: "2023-11-01T22:58:48.262Z",
