        url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dytb4ayqj/image/upload/v1698975126/Screen_Shot_2023-11-02_at_9.31.58_PM_wvefds.png",
        abovewriting:
          "THURSDAY: I didn't work too much on this today. I would guess maybe a half hour. All I did was make an abstract class out of the dialogue script so that I could make multiple instances of them throughout the game without having to copy all the functions and lines of code over and over, and I can adjust the code if I need to in one place.",
        belowwriting: "",
        created_at: "2023-11-03T01:33:20.062Z",
        updated_at: "2023-11-03T01:33:20.062Z",
        post_id: 14,
