        abovewriting: "Also made some trees with tinfoil, wire, and polymer clay.",
        belowwriting:
          "I made five but the photo only has four. This is to make the final version of the set for the forest clearing scenes. I will likely add a painted backdrop to make the forest look more populated and photoshop it until it looks nice. I will need trees for a few different scenes, hopefully I can reuse these ones at different angles? Thinking about testing AI sites to generate a forest full of trees that look like this as well but don't have high hopes for that.",
        created_at: "2023-11-04T16:05:34.181Z",
        updated_at: "2023-11-04T16:05:57.686Z",
