    header: "Merry Christmas! (Week 18)",
    date: "December 19th - December 26th, 2023",
    paragraphs: [],
    images: [
      {
        id: 105,
        name: "",
        url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dytb4ayqj/image/upload/v1703183294/Screen_Shot_2023-12-21_at_1.28.09_PM_vtvcv5.png",
        abovewriting:
          "I feel like I've made some good progress. I made the scripts much more modular and am really happy I did those tutorials on dialogue and quests, not only because the dialogue editor has been extremely helpful and I will definitely use it, but also because I learned a lot about ways to make things run smoothly and without all these one-off scripts I was using before. Hoping this will save me a lot of time as I dive into trying to create a more final, polished game (demo or chapter) to publish.",
        belowwriting:
          "My dilemma is constant, which is the fight between the technical and the creative. I really feel like both sides of me are waiting for the other to take the reins. When I focus on the technical, I get a bit stuck because I don't have the story to flesh it out. When I focus on the creative, I am not thinking in a way that will lend itself to execution. I decided to make a list of simple features (inventory interaction, quests, dialogue, combat) and build the story around the game moments that come from these features. The things I have been expecting myself to create are a bit outside of my experience level and it's been too frustrating. It's like I am not getting along with my coworkers, but I am my only coworker, haha. A good lesson to be aware of being more decisive when I'm working with others to avoid annoying them as I have annoyed myself. Hopefully I will emerge victorious with a great outline for a scene using these simple features. I re-played the first half of Sally Face this week which also gave me some inspiration because it's built in unity and is very simple in the game mechanics.",
        created_at: "2023-12-21T18:33:46.099Z",
        updated_at: "2023-12-21T18:33:46.099Z",
        post_id: 22,
      },
    ],
