        abovewriting:
          "I've decided to do the rigging and animation in Unity, rather than using Moho to export stills. It's much more seamless and I'm able to allow customization of colors more easily.",
        belowwriting:
          "I've already hooked up the character side, front, and glove closeup animations, and enabled saving custom colors this week.",
        created_at: "2024-04-03T23:58:59.808Z",
        updated_at: "2024-04-03T23:58:59.808Z",
