        name: "",
        url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dytb4ayqj/image/upload/v1715297370/Screen_Shot_2024-05-09_at_7.29.24_PM_lgnigf.png",
        abovewriting:
          "It was helpful to come up with this new outline, for some reason it gave me a better feeling/visualization of how to shift the aesthetic of the game and made me more comfortable using real life photos rather than making everything by hand which wasn't creating enough diversity for the way I wanted things to look.",
