        abovewriting:
          'I think it could be argued that it shouldn\'t have been done, but it was a nice procrastination while still adding to my work type of activity, was this garden scene in the maze where the flowers bloom as you get closer to them, and sing a little song that is a nod to the original "laughing" song that I shared in week 32.',
        belowwriting: "",
